<bug>
    <id>97</id>
    <title>Deleting post : confirmation appeared but post was still visible.</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">Nexus 7, 4.2.2</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.2">This was a little weird.</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.3">I tried deleting a post by clicking the trashcan icon.</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.4">I confirmed I wanted to delete the post.</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.5">I saw the toast that the post was deleted.</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.6">However the post was still visible on the screen until the post list refreshed.</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.7">I think the right UX would be to show the toast after the post was removed.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
</bug>
